ygData.messageBody:
Each server is different. On Solusek Ro we don't have many people that go
to Solusek B. Usually just a group of 6 that hangs out there. I saw the
chest go for 80p. The other bronze go for 40p, but they are just so much
easier to get. If you need medium bronze, expect to pay more.
